<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN388-intro">tiṇai, atu. tuṟai, iyaṉmoḻi. ciṟukuṭikiḻāṉpaṇṇaṉai maturai aḷakkarñāḻārmakaṉār maḷḷaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN388">
<l>veḷḷi teṉpulat tuṟaiya viḷaivayaṟ</l>
<l>paḷḷam vāṭiya payaṉil kālai</l>
<l>yirumpaṟaik kiṇaimakaṉ ceṉṟavaṉ perumpeyar</l>
<l><gap quantity="38" reason="lost" unit="character"/> poruntit</l>
<l>taṉṉilai yaṟiyuna ṉāka vannilai</l>
<l>yiṭukka ṇiriyal pōka vuṭaiya</l>
<l>koṭuttō ṉentai koṭaimēn tōṉṟa</l>
<l><gap quantity="37" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ṉāmaruppāka</l>
<l>vellum vāymoḻip pulluṭaip</l>
<l>peyarkkum paṇṇaṉ kēṭṭirō makkireṉa</l>
<l>viṉaippaka ṭēṟṟa mēḻi kiṇaittoṭā</l>
<l>nāṭoṟum pāṭē ṉāyi ṉāṉā</l>
<l>maṇikiḷar muṉṟiṟ ṟeṉṉavaṉ marukaṉ</l>
<l>piṇimura ciraṅkum pīṭukeḻu tāṉai</l>
<l>yaṇṇal yāṉai vaḻuti</l>
<l>kaṇmā ṟiliyareṉ peruṅkiḷaip puravē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“While Venus stays in the southern region, at the yield-less</l>
<l>time when the ditches [between] the ripening paddy field fade, (1f.)</l>
<l corresp="3a-c">as the son of the Kiṇai with the big Paṟai drum, being one who goes, </l>
<l corresp="3d-4">joining ……………. with great name, </l>
<l>[and] one who knows his own state, goes </l>
<l corresp="5-6c">in order to escape the affliction of that state, </l>
<l>the one who gave possessions is our father, an appearance supreme in giving. (6df.)</l>
<l corresp="8">……………………….. as the horn, </l>
<l corresp="10">Did you hear, dullards, of Paṇṇaṉ who moves (x?), </l>
<l corresp="9">with victorious true words, possessing grass?” </l>
<l corresp="11">If, touching [my] Kiṇai drum, about the ploughs accepted by working oxen </l>
<l corresp="12">I don’t sing thus daily without end, </l>
<l corresp="13">may the scion of the Southern king in [his] jewel-shining front yard, </l>
<l corresp="14">with a great army where strapped drums sound, </l>
<l corresp="15">Vāluti on a majestic elephant </l>
<l corresp="16">be without opposition to the protection of my great kin. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
